01:09:50,800 --> 01:09:52,755
Solo ve al taxi.

607
01:09:53,216 --> 01:09:54,269
<i>Hazlo, loco!</i>

608
01:09:54,700 --> 01:09:55,913
Ve a casa

609
01:09:55,948 --> 01:09:56,930
Ya tienes su autógrafo

610
01:09:57,080 --> 01:10:00,759
Ve a casa y ponlo en la pared!

611
01:10:01,000 --> 01:10:02,592
No lo escuches.

